# Firmware image checksum (16-bit additive).
*csum(bytes as Vec of i64, n as i64) returns i64
    s is 0
    i is 0
    while i < n
        s is (s + bytes.get(i)) % 65536
        i is i + 1
    s

*main
    b is vec()
    i is 0
    while i < 256
        b.push(i)
        i is i + 1
    log csum(b, 256)
